Study of the newly registered companies in Northern Norway


A total of 2289 companies were registered in Northern Norway from the first of January 2019 up until the 7th of October 2019.



The region that seems to get most of the newly registered companies every month is Nordland, whereas Finnmark has the lowest amount of companies every month.


The most registrations there was in one month is 143 registrations for the month of January 2019 of the Nordland region.
